        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3214",
        "content": "\"We've been told to keep order, and that no one is to leave their homes or take away a single grain, and that's all about it!\" cried another.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
