        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3214",
        "content": "\"Where's the Elder?\" he cried furiously.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3214_167602_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3214/167602/3214_167602_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3214",
        "content": "\"The Elder....",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3214_167602_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3214/167602/3214_167602_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3214",
        "content": "\"We don't riot, we're following the orders,\" declared Karp, and at that moment several voices began speaking together.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3214_167602_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3214/167602/3214_167602_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3214",
        "content": "\"It's as the old men have decided-there's too many of you giving orders.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
