        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3214",
        "content": "\"You know it has cost money!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3214_167602_000044_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3214/167602/3214_167602_000044_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3214",
        "content": "I don't like that way of doing things.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3214_167602_000044_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3214/167602/3214_167602_000044_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3214",
        "content": "Let it all be done properly, according to rule.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3214_167602_000044_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3214/167602/3214_167602_000044_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3214",
        "content": "Look here, put it under the bast matting and cover it with hay-that's the way!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3214_167602_000045_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3214/167602/3214_167602_000045_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3214",
        "content": "\"Don't catch up against it!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3214_167602_000045_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3214/167602/3214_167602_000045_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3214",
        "content": "It's heavy, lads-solid books.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3214_167602_000048_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3214/167602/3214_167602_000048_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3214",
        "content": "Good bye, Princess.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3214_167602_000055_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3214/167602/3214_167602_000055_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3214",
        "content": "\"Was it not fate that brought him to Bogucharovo, and at that very moment?\" thought Princess Mary.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3214_167602_000056_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3214/167602/3214_167602_000056_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3214",
        "content": "For himself personally Nicholas could not wish for a better wife: by marrying her he would make the countess his mother happy, would be able to put his father's affairs in order, and would even-he felt it-ensure Princess Mary's happiness.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3214_167602_000057_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3214/167602/3214_167602_000057_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3214",
        "content": "But Sonya?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3214_167602_000057_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3214/167602/3214_167602_000057_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3214",
        "content": "And his plighted word?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3214_167606_000011_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3214/167606/3214_167606_000011_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3214",
        "content": "How is it that we are staying on?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3214_167606_000018_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3214/167606/3214_167606_000018_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3214",
        "content": "See!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3214_167606_000019_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3214/167606/3214_167606_000019_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3214",
        "content": "Didn't he write in those idiotic broadsheets that anyone, 'whoever it might be, should be dragged to the lockup by his hair'? (How silly!) 'And honor and glory to whoever captures him,' he says.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3214_167606_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3214/167606/3214_167606_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3214",
        "content": "\"Well then, sell it,\" said he.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3214_167606_000023_000001",
